text: Ruacana Airport is an airport serving Ruacana and the Ruacana hydroelectric power station in the Omusati Region of Namibia. The Ruacana non-directional beacon (Ident: RC) is on the field. ==See also== * * *List of airports in Namibia *Transport in Namibia ==References== ==External links== * OurAirports - Ruacana * Ruacana Airport * OpenStreetMap - Ruacana Category:Airports in Namibia
